Karl Kanga - Hips For Sale (1987) MP3 320


Karl Kanga is a Swedish composer, lyricist, singer, musician (guitar) and label manager. He was acclaimed as the glam rocker in the late 1980s, with some influences from Billy Idol which is sometimes pointed criticism. In the 1990s he was involved as lead singer of blues rock group The Hardliners, who released an album, "The Hardliners Have Arrived" in 1993.
